author: MisterCheezeCake
name: SkyBlockKeybinds
description: A simple, lightweight module that allows you to bind commands to various commands for Hypixel SkyBlock
helpMessage: &aThank you for choosing SkyBlock keybinds! To bind keybinds just open the controls menu. If you would like keybinds added, you can run the command &e/sbkrequest &aor join my Discord with inv.wtf/cheeze
